Often written as {{zh-l|*說}} in pre-Qin texts.

===Etymology===
STEDT compares it to {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*lot||free; release; slip; dislocate}}. Cognate with {{och-l|愉|happy; pleased}}, {{och-l|說|id=1|to speak; to explain}}, {{och-l|脫|to take off (clothes); to escape}}, {{och-l|偷|to steal}}.

